(STORY) 
The police have found out about criminals plans to plant a bomb in the local park. These members of a large, powerful mob have taken possession of dangerous weapons, such as rifles and grenades. Stop them from planting the bomb and kill them off. If you are one of the criminals, kill off the police and plant the bomb. Good luck!
(STORY)

I made this map in about 4 1/2 hours. I hope you all like it. :)
